Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:04.27,N_Pri,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Negi has learned of the vampire girl’s sad past.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:07.61,N_Pri,,0000,0000,0000,,Should she get her hands on Negi’s blood, her magic imprisonment will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.61,0:00:15.32,N_Pri,,0000,0000,0000,,And the vampire girl will be set free to live outside of the Academy borders. The vampire will be set free in a peaceful town.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:17.74,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,We must not let her free.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:19.49,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Takamichi…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:24.87,N_Pri,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking, Negi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:28.38,N_Pri,Person,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you need to stop lazing around, Chamo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:33.67,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,How {\i1}dare {\i0}you underestimate me, Takamichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:35.92,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,So you came after all, Evangeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:39.22,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t let you meet Negi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:42.22,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not the one you should be after.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:46.52,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,They were still roaming around campus at this hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:49.64,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,So I showed them that playing in the dark is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:52.94,N_Nat,Natsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Takahata-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:53.94,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,Get off me! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:55.82,N_Chi,Chizuru,0000,0000,0000,,No means yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:58.11,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,You should get rid of this ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:02:59.49,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Give that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:03.32,N_Aya,Ayaka,0000,0000,0000,,We will give it back if you win a game of old maid, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:05.20,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:08.54,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.96,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of Iinchou-san and the others now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:14.13,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,That's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:20.13,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be fooled! A vampire’s magic naturally disappears at dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:21.38,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it, Takamichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:23.18,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Run while you still can, Negi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.14,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can run away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.35,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-kun…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:41.36,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, we came because you said it was an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:45.53,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Well, isn’t it?! They released a used copy of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:50.08,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,And I finally bought it! Zombie Rider: Son-in-Law Chapter! I’m so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:54.04,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean “I finally bought it!”? You borrowed the money from Konoka-ojousama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.50,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,I said I’d pay her back next month!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:04:00.17,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,Calling us out for something like this…What are we to do if we stay past curfew?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:02.92,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Konoka, have you played this before? It's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:05.18,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no, I’m okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:11.48,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me! If Konoka-ojousama’s character is damaged from this, you’ll be held responsible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:16.86,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(352,333,352,387,600,1080)}You can become the Master of Zombies if you take over the castle, and you'll get 108 Bonnou Boys as your henchmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.65,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say that…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:21.74,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,Would you just LISTEEEEEEN?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:21.74,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Negi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.95,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Negi-kun? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:27.57,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no, no! I mean… I forgot to buy some spring onions!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.83,N_Asu,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I gotta go get some. You’ll have to head on home without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:32.12,N_Asu,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I’ll even leave this to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:35.12,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Wai-! Asuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:38.13,N_Kon,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, she’s always leaving me behind…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:42.88,N_Kon,,0000,0000,0000,,But oh? She doesn’t even know how to cook; what she want with spring onions?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.26,N_Kon,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaddya think, Secchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:48.60,N_Set,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah ha, the Bonnou Boys signifies the amount of Bonnous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.85,N_Set,,0000,0000,0000,,But why a son-in-law?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.60,N_Set,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Secchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:05:01.27,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,Er, I mean… What’s a Master of Zombie, anyway?! Sounds like a bunch of stupid stuff. It really is…! This thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:03.19,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,That’s Asuna’s…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:05.36,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Oh my gosh! I’ll get it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:09.87,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Secchan, if you wanna play the game, then don’t be afraid to honestly say so!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:11.37,N_Kon,,0000,0000,0000,,Son-in-law...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.71,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Negi… When we went together it was last night’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:24.76,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,So you wanna try to run away and learn the truth, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:29.18,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not running away; I just wanted to talk to you personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:30.80,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to me, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:37.56,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve heard about your form from Takamichi. He even said that my father used his magic to imprison you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.73,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Really now? …So?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:44.78,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Evangeline-san… I don’t mind giving my blood to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:45.90,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:48.70,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,But, I want you to promise me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:49.91,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Promise what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:55.70,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I manage to set you free, promise me that you won’t attack anyone ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:06:00.04,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,It’s been 15 years…since they took away your magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:05.05,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,They wouldn’t even let you go past the barrier they made… Wasn’t that painful for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:09.55,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,So please, allow me to free you! I want to set you free!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:16.93,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Aren’t you the kind one. Alright…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.39,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:23.82,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,…or so I’d like to say. I’m sorry you have to pity me, little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:28.19,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really think I’d promise you?! Don’t make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:31.20,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen here; I’m a {\i1}vampire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:38.96,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,That freaking hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:40.42,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a shoe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:43.21,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Negi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:45.38,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Asuna-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:48.59,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dracula! Let go of Negi {\i1}right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:50.43,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Why you… don’t interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:57.02,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,W-why you...! Not the face!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:00.98,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Didn’t I tell you… to let go of Negi!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.27,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Wah! No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.98,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,She’s really gonna throw that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.53,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.36,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:15.12,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Asuna-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.95,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Negi! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:22.21,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am! Thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:27.13,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Um… Sure, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:33.01,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,How {\i1}dare {\i0}you underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:34.18,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Evangeline-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:36.76,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Evangeline? How’s that her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:39.72,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,She’s transformed herself into a vampire, thanks to her magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:46.90,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,It lit up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:48.23,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:20.27,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,The lake…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:24.64,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,She can use frost spells...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:29.02,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t think that I spent these 15 years here sitting around peaceful and quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:33.74,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:34.36,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:37.16,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Asuna-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:38.91,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Owww…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:39.87,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:45.92,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief, that was dangerous, Evangeline!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:51.67,N_Asu,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t care if you’ve got this hot bod from your magic; there’re still things you can and can’t do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:54.47,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,This is payback!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:57.39,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Chachamaru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.97,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,What? You can move now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:02.22,N_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:05.06,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me, Chachamaru! Hey, let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:08.56,N_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,Those who try to hurt my master will be eliminated, regardless if she’s a classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:10.82,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Asuna-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:23.54,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. So he’s the type to run away when he can. Let’s go, Chachamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.46,N_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:29.46,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Asuna-san! Asuna-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.17,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,Asuna-san! Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:34.67,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,You have no choice but to do a provisional contract, Aniki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:36.88,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Chamo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:39.64,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting for the right moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:42.81,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, Aniki, do a provisional contract! Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.68,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,A provisional contract? With Asuna-san…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:47.94,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Eh… but…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:51.52,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,No time to be hot n’ bothered! The enemy’s nearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:54.78,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,You’re right. We probably have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:56.19,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Asuna-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:58.45,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,That’s my Ane-san! You’re quick to pick up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:02.41,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Negi, if we don’t do this we can’t win. Make a provisional contract with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:04.24,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:05.70,N_2,Asuna and Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,HURRY UP!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:06.45,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:07.50,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Ack! Up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:15.88,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,I found you~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:26.77,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Can’t run now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:36.11,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Uhyaa~ My feet are so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:38.40,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Here, use my shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:39.82,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I’ll wear ‘em!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.99,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.82,0:10:44.28,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,But… thanks anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:48.79,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Asuna-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:53.46,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Great mood! Okay, let’s get started on that provisional contract asap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:55.88,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,PACTIO!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.93,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it’s so warm…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:03.97,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Magic from the heart gives off heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.31,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Wow… it feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:10.56,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Save the explanations! We’ve got something to take care of and fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:11.73,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:16.86,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Ane-san! Kiss him! Kiss him! Just kiss him already! Kiss! Kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:18.61,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it with the “Kiss kiss” crap, you stupid rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:21.82,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I’m {\i1}not {\i0}a rat! You violent girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:27.95,N_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:28.95,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:33.21,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Um… I’m sorry. I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:36.38,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Asuna-san, it’s coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.13,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.11,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,WROOOOOOOOONG!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:07.70,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t kiss him there! Give him a {\i1}real {\i0}kiss! It ain’t gonna work if you don’t kiss his lips!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:08.95,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? His lips?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:10.83,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.00,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Does it look like I care?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:14.92,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Think about other people! This’ll be my first kiss, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:18.34,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Ane-san, how old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:19.55,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Noisy brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:27.51,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:31.47,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Aigh, Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:40.69,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Whoo! You did it, Ane-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:47.74,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Provisional Contract Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:54.21,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. Exchanged a provisional contract, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:56.96,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec! I haven’t changed a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:58.88,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,No, you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:05.80,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Partner: Kagurazaka Asuna. Show me the power within you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:25.69,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Contract… Activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.46,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Uwaaah! Freaking awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:55.14,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,This is… I feel like I’m full of power all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:59.48,N_Asu,,0000,0000,0000,,I can win. With this, I can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:18.25,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,You’re pretty damn good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.33,N_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,Why, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:27.76,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve done it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:35.68,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can run away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:37.93,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,W-wait! Ane-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:40.27,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Chachamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:45.52,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Ane-san! Where’re you going?! What’re ya gonna do if you just leave your partner Negi alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:49.61,N_Kam,,0000,0000,0000,,Oiiiii!... she’s gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:51.86,N_Kam,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always doing what she wants and leaves us out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:54.53,N_Kam,,0000,0000,0000,,No point in doing a provisional contract now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:59.79,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,What a dependable partner you have, eh Negi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:04.25,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Now… shall I take your blood now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:08.01,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn’t keep that promise, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:12.80,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,I live the way I want to. That’s the freedom I wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:13.93,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Fine…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:14.93,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Aniki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:16.97,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Chamo-kun, it’s going to get bad, so steer clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:17.72,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Yessir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:40.54,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,You may be the son of the Thousand Master… but in the end, you’re still a mere child.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:47.00,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, allow me to take it… I can finally indulge in my newfound freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:49.30,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Aniki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:54.39,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Ow ow ow ow ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:56.35,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Why you little-!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:00.85,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.83,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Evangeline-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:26.79,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand Master! I’ll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:30.63,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,Mark my words, I’ll get my revenge someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:34.05,N_Neg,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Open your eyes, Evangeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:42.72,N_Neg,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Live in the light. Feel the light. Your future lies there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:58.28,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,The light… it’s so warm…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:13.63,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:24.14,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you are my student, aren’t you, Evangeline-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:54.42,N_Pri,Dean,0000,0000,0000,,What? It’s over already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:56.97,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Dean, Takamichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:03.93,N_Pri,Dean,0000,0000,0000,,Evangeline, now you understand why you were put here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:09.65,N_Pri,Dean,0000,0000,0000,,Though, your heart already knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.19,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:18.74,N_Pri,Dean,0000,0000,0000,,Why, last night, you brought the damaged Chachamaru in for repair. You would have never done so in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:24.49,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, School Dean, I don’t think I ever-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.70,0:18:34.17,N_Neg,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Live in the light. Feel the light. Your future lies there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:39.88,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,The light, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.48,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Asuna-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:53.31,N_Cha,Chachamaru,0000,0000,0000,,It seems her energy has drained.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:58.15,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Waah, I’m hungry! I can’t move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:06.20,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Chachamaru, we’re going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:07.41,N_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:09.20,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Evangeline-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:14.13,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t get the wrong idea, Negi. It’s not like I gave up in getting your blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:18.71,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,I suggest you be careful on the next full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:24.72,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Evangeline-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:27.01,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,It’ll be fine, Negi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:28.31,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Takamichi…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:32.64,N_Pri,Dean,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, Negi, do something about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:42.99,N_Nek,Nekane,0000,0000,0000,,Negi, it seems like you’re working hard and doing just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:46.32,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m actually kind of surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:52.92,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be a little angry if I said this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:57.09,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,but I thought I’d get a letter from you right away, saying that you’d want to go back to Wales.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:09.06,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m so glad that you’ve met wonderful people over there. It makes me happy to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:17.90,N_Nek,Nekane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that’s right! I got a letter from Anya, who is in London right now. She seems to be happy and doing just fine as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:20.19,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that she’d never lose to you, Negi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:29.62,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,I should conclude this now. I hope your training goes well! I love you, Negi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:32.08,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:40.46,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:42.17,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,From here on out, you are all 9th graders!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:45.72,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a pleasure to be with you for another year!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:49.22,N_2,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,The pleasure’s ours, Negi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:21:00.48,N_Pri,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Negi Springfield, child middle school teacher and mage extraordinaire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:07.36,N_Pri,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,This is where our story begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:53.72,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why can’t I ever finish my introduction?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.05,0:22:56.18,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Man, don’t cry…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:22:58.77,N_Kae,Kaede,0000,0000,0000,,We don’t have time for this, de gozaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.77,0:23:01.44,N_Kuu,Kuu Fei,0000,0000,0000,,We still have an enemy waiting for us, aru!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.44,0:23:03.52,N_Yue,Yue,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, we should summon a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:06.48,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,But me! I’m just… I’m just a…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.48,0:23:09.90,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Makie, how about {\i1}you {\i0}start out the introductions? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:14.37,N_Yue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that is a great idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.57,0:23:16.58,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,I can lead the introductions? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:19.66,N_Kae,Kaede,0000,0000,0000,,If you want. We’re not gonna fuss over a minor order change de gozaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.66,0:23:22.79,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.12,0:23:24.29,N_Kuu,Kuu Fei,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:26.29,N_2,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Mahora Sentai Baka Ranger!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.29,0:23:27.71,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone gets along! Baka Pi-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.05,0:23:33.82,N_Yue,Yue,0000,0000,0000,,The robot has arrived.
